commit.message:
pamu2fcfg: make_cred() for non-PIN authenticators

CTAP2.0 with some form of UV configured will require UV for credential
creation.  Similarly, CTAP2.1 devices will require some form of UV if
the makeCredUvNotRqd option is not enabled.

While here, allow fallback to PIN if built-in UV is blocked.
